name: MercuryTrade
description: MercuryTrade is an overlay application for Path of Exile written in Java. Initially designed to facilitate trading interactions, today it's an immense platform that drastically improves user experience for the players.

name: POE TradeMacro
description: PoE TradeMacro is an Autohotkey (AHK) script that provides several convenient QoL features for Path of Exile Trading.
